<li>Mascarenhas, S. and Agarwal, M., 2021, November. A comparison between VGG16, VGG19 and ResNet50 architecture frameworks for Image Classification. In 2021 International Conference on Disruptive Technologies for Multi-Disciplinary Research and Applications (CENT- CON) (Vol. 1, pp. 96-99). IEEE.</li>
